Based on the specifications of Heini Schawalder and Maurice Ducret, the development for the ANR scoring and visualisation software was initiated during 2009-2010 at the Commercial and Industrial Training college (GIBBS) Bern, Switzerland. Under the technical lead of Luc Baumann/SharpSoft (who has been with the the project from its very beginnings) numerous changes and improvements were implemented in the following years.
